descript.abstract: This data set is known as Boundary Jurisdiction Annexations abbreviated ANNEX and contains the annexation polygons for the City of Bakersfield, CA since 1965. All annexation polygons are grouped by year into regions defining the City of Bakersfield, CA city limits.
descript.purpose: The data set was created to aid in local GIS and mapping applications and to allow the visualizations of city growth over the years.
